@23 = ~Gulp!~
@24 = ~Expired:~

@31 = ~Potion of Battlefield Lust~
@32 = ~Once consumed, this potion will cause a surge of energy to travel through the body raising the drinker's prowess in combat. This provides all the bonuses of a faster and preciser attack for the duration of the effect, which is 15 turns.
Multiple potions have only partial benefits.

Weight: 1

Not usable by:
 Wizard Slayer~

@33 = ~Mage's Draught Potion~
@34 = ~Once consumed, this potion will cause a surge of energy to travel through the mind allowing the drinker's spells to be remembered.

STATISTICS:

- Recalls one spell of each level from 1 through 5.

Weight: 1

Only usable by:
 Mage~

@35 = ~Assassin's Gift~
@36 = ~Once consumed, this potion will cause a surge of energy to travel through the body raising the drinker's ability to backstab for the duration of the effect, which is 15 turns.

STATISTICS:

- 2 backstab level bonus
- THAC0 set to 0.

Weight: 1

Only usable by:
 Thief~

@37 = ~Potion of Ogre Power~
@38 = ~Once consumed, this potion will cause a surge of energy to travel through the body raising the drinker's skills to inflict maximum damage on every hit for the duration of the effect, which is 15 turns.

STATISTICS:

Weight: 1

Not usable by:
 Wizard Slayer~

@39 = ~Potion of Mind Shield~
@40 = ~This potion will maintain clarity and order from encroaching chaos and insanity. After drinking this potion, the imbiber feels an overwhelming feeling of calm and purpose, such that he will be unaffected by threatening influences such as feeblemind, confusion, charm, horror, stun, hold, morale failure and unconsciousness, but you still can get drunk! This feeling will last for the duration of the enchantment or until dispelled.

STATISTICS:

- Special: Prevents feeblemind, confusion, fear, charm, stun, hold and unconsciousness.
  Duration: 15 turns

Weight: 1

Not usable by:
 Wizard Slayer~

@41 = ~Magic Ward~
@42 = ~Drinking this potion imbues the person with a strong magical protection, enhancing the chances to resist spells more effectively.

STATISTICS:

- Saving Throws: +5
  Duration: 1 day

Weight: 1

Not usable by:
 Wizard Slayer~

@43 = ~Gatekeeper~
@44 = ~Once consumed, this potion will cause a surge of energy to travel through the body enabling the drinker to defend against entombment-like spells and effects for 1 hour.

STATISTICS:

Weight: 1

Not usable by:
 Wizard Slayer~

@45 = ~Heal~
@46 = ~Once consumed, this potion will cause a surge of energy to travel through the body allowing the drinker to regain any lost health, effectively curing all physical damage suffered.

STATISTICS:

- Special: Restores all Hit Points.

Weight: 1~


